                      <div class="u-row-container content" style="padding: 35px; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242)">
                        <p style="font-size: 15px;">Dear Admin Team and Andrew Frentz, </p>
                        <p  style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15px;">A new REALTOR® intake form has been submitted by a prospective REALTOR® who wishes to join Real Estate Professionals Inc. Please review the details below:</p>
                    
                      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15px;"><strong>REALTOR® Information:</strong></p>
                        <ul> 
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">First Name: {{ $first_name }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Last Name: {{ $last_name }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Phone Number: {{ $phone }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Email: {{ $email }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Are You New to the Industry?: {{ $joinee ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">What is the Best Way to Contact You?: {{ $contact ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Years & Months of Experience: {{ $experience ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">What Areas Are You Licensed In?: {{ $licensed_area ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Are you currently a member/will be a member of a real estate board? If yes, please specify : 
                            {{ $board_name ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">What Areas Do You Want to Practice?: {{ $practice_areas ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">How Did you Find Real Estate Professionals Inc.?: {{ $perceive ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">Who Referred You to Real Estate Professionals Inc.?: {{ $reference ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                          <li style="font-size: 15px;">What about Real Estate Professionals Inc. Interests You the Most?: {{ $about ?? 'N/A' }}</li>
                       
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Action Required:</strong></p>
                        <ul> 
                        <li style="font-size: 15px;">Please review the attached intake form for further details.</li>
                        <li style="font-size: 15px;">If everything is in order, proceed with onboarding the new REALTOR®.</li>
                        <li style="font-size: 15px;">  If any additional information is required, please contact the REALTOR® directly at {{$email }} or {{$phone }}.</li>
                      </ul>
                      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Contact Information:</strong></p>
                      <ul> 
                      <li style="font-size: 15px;">Admin Email: <a href="mailto:marketing@repinc.ca">marketing@repinc.ca</a></li>
                      <li style="font-size: 15px;">Andrew Frentz's Email: <a href="mailto:andrewfrentz@repinc.ca">andrewfrentz@repinc.ca</a></li>
                    </ul>
                      <p style="margin-top: 15px;  font-size: 15px;">Should you have any questions or need further clarification, please reach out.</p>
                      <p style="margin-top: 15px;  font-size: 15px;">Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
                        <p  style="margin-top: 15px;  font-size: 15px;">Best regards, </p>
                        <p  style="margin-top: 15px;  font-size: 15px;">Team, Real Estate Professionals Inc. </p>
